<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-10 medium-offset-2 columns">
    <h2>How to Y2Q</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="small-12 medium-10 medium-offset-2 columns">
    <h3>In 90 seconds, we want to hear the answer to 3 questions:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>What breaks your heart?</li>
      <li>What makes you come alive?</li>
      <li>How are you (or will you) put these two together?</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .blurb-number-1::before {
    content: "1";
    font-weight:bold;
  }
  .blurb-number-2::before {
    content: "2";
    font-weight:bold;
  }
  .blurb-number-3::before {
    content: "3";
    font-weight:bold;
  }
</style>

<div class="row">
  <%= render layout: "shared/components/blurb", locals: { blurb_title: "Reflect", icon_class: "fa fa-2x blurb-number-1" } do %>
    <p>Think about what breaks your heart and what makes you come alive.</p>
  <% end %>
  <%= render layout: "shared/components/blurb", locals: { blurb_title: "Record", icon_class: "fa fa-2x blurb-number-2" } do %>
    <p>Upload a video to YouTube telling us how you are (or will) put these two together.</p>
  <% end %>
  <%= render layout: "shared/components/blurb", locals: { blurb_title: "Submit", icon_class: "fa fa-2x blurb-number-3" } do %>
    <p>Submit your video to Y2Q using the form below.</p>
  <% end %>
</div>
